{"tid":572741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車廂激戰】洋漢地鐵吸煙被阻 爆粗鬧中國客：Animal","createTime":"2018-02-25T23:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T15:08:36.000Z","uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"35ae1b428fafe7729e07d82240552f124a8cb3fa","tid":572741,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T23:41:40.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲都有膽過港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵車箱不可飲食、吸煙是基本常識，可是北京地鐵車箱內，竟有一名金髮碧眼的洋人，在車箱內吞雲吐霧，有乘客見到上前阻止，卻被回以粗口「Fxxking Animal（動物）」，勸阻乘客亦用英文粗口反擊，雙方陷入一場口水戰。有網民見，洋漢腳步浮浮，疑似是「喝多了」。<br />\n<br />\n昨日，微博用戶@Jg_賈吾佳在網上發文、影片，指「一個老外在北京地鐵2號線上抽煙，幾個乘客制止他，他就開始罵人狂噴（罵）fxxking animal。學好英語真的很重要，我只說了一句Put out ur（your）cigarette or leave China，旁邊一兄弟直接開始機關槍式的對噴，還有一（個）哥們直接衝上去把他煙搶了！」<br />\n<br />\n影片所見，一名洋漢手中拿着一枝煙，畫外音有說：「fxxk off Back to your country, OK?」（滾回你的國家，可以嗎？），洋漢腳步浮浮、語無倫次，激動說「It's not a country. It's called the Middle Kingdom」（它不是一個國家，它叫做中國），及後用粗口罵阻止他吸煙的人。<br />\n<br />\n有目撃者表示，該名外國人從宣武門站開始吵起來，說着說着就在車箱內遊走，手上煙一直沒熄，到了復興門站，就有一名女職員上車調停，而洋漢手上的煙是被一個年輕男子搶走弄熄的。<br />\n<br />\n網民看片後議論紛紛，說「老外看來不懂英文。假如懂，地鐵車門上貼的禁止吸煙，簡直就是白搭」、「沒素質 丟人丟到外國了」、「喝多了吧？走路還晃悠，把這裡當他家了」、「是不是喝醉了？或是嗑藥了？看着他不清醒，暈暈的感覺」。"},{"pid":"c33e27c8e131144687df87ccc3fb43964abc6295","tid":572741,"uid":172940,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T00:47:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d89abebb27fc03cef14e9a313eebc0cc2f5db15b","tid":572741,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T00:48:39.000Z","msg":"打柒佢啦"},{"pid":"0c994a0f71abb6b9327be42caeb527e322cc7531","tid":572741,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T00:49:06.000Z","msg":"換著港豬<br />\n除左影相up fb 仲識點"},{"pid":"d08af827ffc22ece0f20b8e6d3a4348b67216648","tid":572741,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T00:49:49.000Z","msg":"原來係北京地頭 以為係香港都咁正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0678b9bc7ab5830bb23c6f12704454b996b025bf","tid":572741,"uid":116688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T00:50:48.000Z","msg":"果晚即刻有大把女錫返啦冇事㗎喎"},{"pid":"78b9ed73747fe0fd9486cdf55d302e27be7c876b","tid":572741,"uid":35964,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"個鬼佬好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a14729746e99b8ac4b564cde05bb4366132c75","tid":572741,"uid":23833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0c994a0f71abb6b9327be42caeb527e322cc7531","tid":572741,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T00:49:06.000Z","msg":"換著港豬<br />\n除左影相up fb 仲識點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"影相放上連登隻萬人之力聲討到1001然後結束"},{"pid":"83c839392693663553b0845f09a1b1b3d5f8f3c8","tid":572741,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029ec61ffdacd6678dd0acae1c630ce035b0248e","tid":572741,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"Middle Kingdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0c8154464d3d349902f0eb62a4192401cc52a8","tid":572741,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"死洋鬼子，咱們這裡是只能吐痰不能抽煙的"},{"pid":"65d52be94d23ee71dde16fdcd0f41158a4d908e7","tid":572741,"uid":72000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"符合國情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk